quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"BY THE Fig, and by the Olive"
  95,2,By Mount Sinai
  95,3,and by this inviolate city.²
  95,4,We created man in a most noble image
  95,5,and then We shall reduce him to the lowest of the low
  95,6,"except those who believe and do good works, for theirs shall be a boundless recompense"
  95,7,What then after this can make you deny the Last Judgement
  95,8,Is God not the most just of judges